{"questionId":"27814","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Sergio is interested in whether an adult’s favourite breakfast berry depends on their income&nbsp;level. He obtains the following data for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>341</mn></math> adults and decides to carry out a <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> test for&nbsp;independence, at the <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>10</mn><mo>%</mo></math> significance level.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/98010bfec5dc8554d5e625ed72dfcb4c6665d0df.png\"></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the value of the <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math> statistic.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>27</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>26821</mn><mo>…</mo></mrow></mfenced></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A2</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"27814","referenceCode":"22N.1.SL.TZ0.4b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the value of the χ2 statistic.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.11—Expected, observed, hypotheses, chi squared, gof, t-test"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}